sequenceDiagram
  actor User as Пользователь
  participant UI as UI (Flet)
  participant UC as Use case: AddTransaction
  participant Repo as TransactionRepository
  participant DB as SQLite

  User->>UI: Заполнить форму (сумма, дата, категория)
  UI->>UC: submit(data)
  UC->>UC: validate(data)
  UC->>Repo: create(transaction)
  Repo->>DB: INSERT INTO transactions (...)
  DB-->>Repo: OK (id)
  Repo-->>UC: transaction_id
  UC-->>UI: success
  UI-->>User: Транзакция добавлена

